{
  "_readme": [
    "This one file drives the whole comparison tool. Edit it, commit, done.",
    "",
    "affiliateTag  Amazon Associates tag. While empty, buy buttons are hidden",
    "              entirely so the site never ships untagged links.",
    "",
    "DO NOT put prices in here. Amazon requires displayed prices to be",
    "refreshed or removed within 24 hours. Use the budget band instead and let",
    "Amazon show the live price.",
    "",
    "SPECS COME FROM EACH PRODUCT'S OWN AMAZON TITLE, which is tied to that",
    "exact ASIN. The Features & Specs table on Amazon is NOT reliable on",
    "listings with variants: the UtechSmart Venus table reports Bluetooth /",
    "wireless / 70hr while its own title says wired. Always cross-check.",
    "",
    "Fields per product:",
    "  id        short unique slug",
    "  name      product name",
    "  category  must match a category id below",
    "  group     heading for the comparison chart, e.g. MMO Mice",
    "  budget    must match a budget id below",
    "  asin      the 10 character code in the Amazon URL after /dp/",
    "  specs     any key/value pairs. Keys shared across products line up as",
    "            rows in the chart, so keep naming consistent.",
    "  verdict   optional. Leave empty unless it is a real opinion.",
    "  pick      optional. true marks it as a recommendation."
  ],

  "affiliateTag": "nexedge-20",

